-- Mexico Searches for 17 Missing Parents and Kids, Milenio Says
-- B y   N a c h a   C a t t a n
-- 2011-12-22T19:32:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-22/mexico-searches-for-17-missing-parents-and-kids-milenio-says.html
The government of the Mexican state
of Guerrero confirmed it is searching for 17 people, among them
nine children, who were reported kidnapped, the newspaper
Milenio reported today.  Gunmen were seen entering three homes on Dec. 11 with high-
powered rifles and abducting the families, according to the
police report filed by a relative of the missing people, Ignacio
Salto Villa, Mexico City-based Milenio said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nacha Cattan in Mexico City at 
 ncattan@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Joshua Goodman  at 
 jgoodman19@bloomberg.net . 